          <li><span><span class="compare-step-num">4.</span> Wait for agent to finish</span> <span class="compare-step-time">blocked</span></li>
          <li><span><span class="compare-step-num">5.</span> Review output, create PR</span> <span class="compare-step-time">manual</span></li>
