      <h2 class="section-heading">View from your phone, anywhere</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">The dashboard runs on your machine. Reach it from your phone over LAN, SSH, Tailscale, ngrok, or self-hosted Piko.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="int-grid">
      <div class="int-card">
        <div class="int-icon" style="color: var(--accent);">
