        <h4>LAN bind</h4>
        <p>Set <code style="font-size:11px; background:var(--bg-elevated); padding:1px 4px; border-radius:3px;">server.host: 0.0.0.0</code> in <code style="font-size:11px; background:var(--bg-elevated); padding:1px 4px; border-radius:3px;">WORKFLOW.md</code>. Browse from any device on the same WiFi.</p>
