        <div class="int-icon" style="color: var(--teal);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><polyline points="4 12 1 9 4 6"/><polyline points="14 12 17 9 14 6"/><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="17" y2="9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>SSH tunnel</h4>
        <p>Forward the port over SSH: <code style="font-size:11px; background:var(--bg-elevated); padding:1px 4px; border-radius:3px;">ssh -L 8090:localhost:8090 host</code>. Familiar to developers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="int-card">
        <div class="int-icon" style="color: var(--accent-strong);">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="7"/><line x1="2" y1="9" x2="16" y2="9"/><path d="M9 2a10 10 0 0 1 0 14M9 2a10 10 0 0 0 0 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Tailscale</h4>
        <p>Zero-config WireGuard mesh. Install on phone + laptop, browse via the tailnet hostname from anywhere in the world.</p>
      </div>
